
= a grassroots initiative that aims to promote open access to civic data of the City of Gatineau

URL = http://gatineauouverte.org/

=Description=

We believe that access to data and information increases civic engagement, making services more accessible and facilitates innovation.

Our primary objective is to ensure that the City of Gatineau puts in place an open data policy and an open data portal. This policy must comply with the standards adopted by other cities in Canada and around the world.

